Process input files sequentially to control memory. Validate/coerce types explicitly.
On irreparable records, skip and log to CSV with full original columns + timestamp,file,line,error.
Emit metrics: rows_ok, rows_skipped, parse_errors. Ensure idempotent DB writes.
